<BaseLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure" description="How Cmprly makes money and why you can trust our recommendations.">
  <div style="max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;padding:2rem 1rem;">
    <h1 style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:1rem;">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p style="font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1rem;">
      <strong>Cmprly participates in affiliate marketing programs.</strong> This means that when you click on some of the links on this site and make a purchase, we may earn a commission — at no extra cost to you.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1rem;">
      Our affiliate relationships include programs through <strong>PartnerStack</strong>, <strong>Impact</strong>, <strong>CJ Affiliate</strong>, and individual SaaS company affiliate programs.
    </p>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.5rem;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem;">Our Commitment to You</h2>
    <ul style="margin-left:1.5rem;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.75;">
      <li>We <strong>never</strong> let affiliate commissions influence our rankings or recommendations.</li>
      <li>Every comparison is based on publicly verifiable data — official pricing pages, feature documentation, and independent benchmarks.</li>
      <li>When we earn a commission on a tool, we tell you. There are no hidden paid placements.</li>
      <li>We disclose our affiliate relationships on every page that contains affiliate links.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.5rem;margin:2rem 0 0.75rem;">FTC Compliance</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.75;">
      In accordance with FTC guidelines, every article on Cmprly that includes affiliate links contains a clear, prominent disclosure at the top of the article. We believe transparency is the foundation of trust — and trust is the foundation of good recommendations.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#6b7280;margin-top:2rem;">Last updated: July 2026</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
